WEBVTT

00:00:01.541 --> 00:00:10.926
Good morning, family! How are you all doing today? Praise the Lord, I'm excited to be here. We have some work to do in the spirit realm.

00:00:10.927 --> 00:00:19.360
I was praying about my video, and I felt the Lord correct me regarding my video about Elon Musk.

00:00:19.361 --> 00:00:29.083
The Lord, after I made that video, I had that itchy feeling and knew the Holy Spirit wasn't pleased completely with it.

00:00:29.084 --> 00:01:00.227
He said, "Brandon, I revealed this stuff to you and told you about his technology that will be used in the Tribulation."I said, "Yes, sir, you did."I saw the demonic spirit that was influencing his mind to help him because he has a genius IQ.

00:01:00.228 --> 00:01:10.734
When you see all that in the spirit, you start linking him with the Antichrist and making him into a bad person, saying he's going to create all this stuff.

00:01:10.735 --> 00:01:24.024
It has to be created; prophecy will be fulfilled because it is prophecy from the Lord telling us what's coming in the future, and somebody had to fill that position.

00:01:24.025 --> 00:01:31.527
He's not the Antichrist, ladies and gentlemen; he is the creator of the Beast system.

00:01:31.528 --> 00:01:38.495
It does not mean that Elon Musk will implement the system; he's just creating it.

00:01:38.496 --> 00:01:47.186
So the Lord said to me, "Brandon, you've got to think bigger."I asked, "What do you want, Lord?

00:01:47.188 --> 00:02:15.618
What are you asking?"He said to me, "Believe that Starlink, the internet system, will be used for good instead of for bad."He said that technology can be used to spread the Gospel throughout the whole world where they don't have internet access.

00:02:15.619 --> 00:02:34.694
He said there are ways to use this as a tool for the Gospel. He said the man is blessed and told me to pray that he would get born again and help the Kingdom of God.

00:02:34.695 --> 00:02:57.215
He said, "You painted him out to be an enemy when he's already trying to help the Republican party, bringing in free speech, and doing what he did."He said there's already a door open and told me to push it wide open and believe God for his soul.

00:02:57.216 --> 00:03:07.457
Let's call him saved today, ladies and gentlemen. Let's pray that he has a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:03:07.458 --> 00:03:22.434
His technology will be used, I believe, but wouldn't it be amazing if Elon Musk got radically born again and started preaching the Gospel like another Billy Graham throughout the whole world?

00:03:22.435 --> 00:03:34.745
He is an evangelist; he has a charisma about him that draws people to him and his social media.

00:03:34.746 --> 00:03:41.369
Just think of what he could do for the Kingdom of God if we started praying for him to get radically saved.

00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:57.202
He's around Trump, and I believe with all my heart Trump is going to have a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ and get baptized in the Holy Ghost in these next four years.

00:03:57.203 --> 00:04:01.051
President Trump can influence him to help him get born again.

00:04:01.052 --> 00:04:11.378
There are so many avenues here, so I want to repent even to you all for some of the things I said.

00:04:11.379 --> 00:04:21.105
You see in part and hear in part as I am growing in my own gifting.

00:04:21.106 --> 00:04:37.826
Several days later, the Lord said to me, "Brandon, you're missing it; I want you to believe me for bigger."So I have to tell you, ladies and gentlemen, let's turn that around.

00:04:37.827 --> 00:04:46.615
I'm not attacking the man anymore. The Lord said, "You don't know where he's at with me; you don't know his soul.

00:04:46.616 --> 00:04:53.559
You judged him because of what you saw in the spirit when I was trying to show you something.

00:04:53.560 --> 00:05:06.242
I showed you part of something, but it doesn't mean you have the whole picture."Again, it's immaturity on my part, and I want to say this: let's intercede for the man and his family.

00:05:06.243 --> 00:05:18.283
It grieved me; I passed judgment in my heart saying he's damned to hell because he's creating the Beast system, and the Lord said, "You don't know that.

00:05:18.284 --> 00:05:32.260
Who are you to say that?"When the Holy Spirit corrects you, it really makes you feel a certain way.

00:05:32.261 --> 00:05:41.745
I told all these 160,000 people who watched that video, and they're all saying they knew he was bad.

00:05:41.746 --> 00:05:56.027
I get it; when you see the Beast system, you relate evil with that and think you can't pray for him.

00:05:56.028 --> 00:06:41.337
When the Lord said to me, "Call him saved, believe for his soul,"I said, "God help me."That's my heart today: to turn this ship for that man and for his family, that they would have a radical visitation from the Lord Jesus Christ and a real conversion.

00:06:41.338 --> 00:06:50.034
We're still believing for the House. We see what the enemy is trying to do, folks, but greater is He that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:06:50.035 --> 00:07:03.557
We're going to take authority over the House again today and believe God for a supernatural visitation over America.

00:07:03.558 --> 00:07:19.197
I was going to go a whole different direction today about the economy and what the Lord is telling me to pray for over the next 70-some days.

00:07:19.198 --> 00:07:38.402
I saw some of the enemy's tactics regarding the dollar, Putin, and Xi Jinping.

00:07:38.403 --> 00:07:52.572
There's a lot of work to be done. I made a mistake, so let's pray for him to get radically born again.

00:07:52.572 --> 00:07:59.477
Believe with all your heart because he could be a major tool for the Kingdom of the Lord.

00:07:59.478 --> 00:08:12.090
What the devil meant for bad, God can turn for good today. Wouldn't it be amazing if Starlink were a tool for the Gospel?

00:08:12.091 --> 00:08:34.304
The devil might try to use it later, but we could use it now for the glory of God.

00:08:34.305 --> 00:08:50.287
The Lord said, "You've got to believe bigger; you think too small."Elon Musk saved! I can see it.

00:08:50.288 --> 00:09:04.070
Elon Musk born again, radically baptized in the Holy Ghost, praying in other tongues, laying hands on the sick, and seeing them recover.

00:09:04.071 --> 00:09:18.965
Proclaiming Jesus Christ as Lord and having a company as a tithe machine to Jesus to help fund churches.

00:09:18.966 --> 00:09:34.852
It could happen. I prayed for Kanye West for years, and though he's having a hard time now, I'm still praying for him.

00:09:34.853 --> 00:09:55.409
I prayed for years for radical conversions for Kim Kardashian and all of them because they influence the world; why not influence the world for Jesus?

00:09:55.410 --> 00:10:01.195
God uses celebrities like Justin Bieber to bring in the harvest.

00:10:01.196 --> 00:10:21.019
It's time for Hollywood and influencers to come to Jesus. Wouldn't it be amazing if Taylor Swift got radically saved?

00:10:21.020 --> 00:10:42.078
She's serving the devil now, but imagine if she were born again, speaking in tongues, and talking about the fire in her music as a Christian artist.

00:10:42.079 --> 00:10:49.181
We have a lot of power on this YouTube channel with all of us praying together.

00:10:49.182 --> 00:11:26.565
Let's be an army for Jesus. I've talked enough; let's pray. You can take your communion; I'll pray alongside you.

00:11:26.566 --> 00:11:38.505
Father, we lift up the body before you and thank you for the communion.

00:11:38.506 --> 00:11:49.887
Your body was broken and beaten for us, and by your stripes we are healed.

00:11:49.888 --> 00:12:08.807
We lift it up and thank you, Father, that you were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities.

00:12:08.808 --> 00:12:26.598
We say no sickness or disease can come near us because it violates our covenant of health.

00:12:26.599 --> 00:13:10.062
Father, I thank you for the blood that covers us and eradicates our sin.

00:13:10.063 --> 00:13:27.382
We plead the blood of Jesus over us today from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:13:27.383 --> 00:13:39.686
Now, Lord, we lift up Elon Musk and I call him saved in the name of Jesus.

00:13:39.687 --> 00:14:16.327
I command the enemy to release his life and speak a radical visitation from you. Manifest yourself to him in a supernatural way.

00:14:16.328 --> 00:14:38.119
I thank you that Elon Musk's eyes are open and that the eyes of his understanding would be enlightened. I speak to his eyes right now that they are no longer blind.

00:14:38.120 --> 00:15:17.382
It doesn't matter what he thinks now; we call laborers across his path and a stirring in his spirit like a furnace.

00:15:17.383 --> 00:15:39.900
In the name of Jesus, he would be a voice for the Lord Jesus Christ. I'm going to pray in the spirit for him now.

00:15:39.901 --> 00:15:43.503
We call the breaking of darkness off of his life in the name of Jesus.

00:15:43.504 --> 00:24:07.813
We pray over his eyes. I see his heart, Lord. We thank you, Father, that he is radically born again today.

00:24:07.814 --> 00:24:40.016
Everyone wants to be loved and accepted. Holy Spirit, move on the man.

00:24:40.017 --> 00:25:00.639
We call the bondage and baggage of life to break off of him today.

00:25:00.640 --> 00:25:17.101
Any darkness or people influencing him, we call them to be removed in Jesus'name.

00:25:17.102 --> 00:26:08.657
I see a specific darkness regarding a woman; Satan, you've been found out.

00:26:08.658 --> 00:27:27.579
Thank you, Holy Spirit, for showing me more. We will pray for Elon Musk for the next 20 days.

00:27:27.580 --> 00:27:53.905
Now, Lord, we pray over this House. We call for a breakthrough in the House seats.

00:27:53.906 --> 00:31:12.027
